--- title: "Overview" author: "Joey Stanley" date: 2023-10-23 date-modified: last-modified --- This page just has a summary of all the hymns and their frequency stats, including the new hymns. I will update this page regularly as I collect more data. ## Quick Facts I currently have data from 71,826 sacrament meetings. If you were to attend that many, it would take about 1496 years---so, more than a couple lifetimes' worth of data. It's also the equivalent of the entire 40-year lifetime of the 1985 hymnal in 37 wards. This data comes from 3,025 wards, mostly in the United States. Across all these meetings, there are 229,521 hymns.
